SUBSTITUTE FOR
SENATE BILL NO. 865
A bill to make, supplement, and adjust appropriations for the
department of military and veterans affairs for the fiscal years
ending September 30, 2026 and September 30, 2027; and to provide
for the expenditure of the appropriations.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
